            <div class="SCXW175149179 BCX8">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">Design </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW175149179 BCX8">Thinking</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">: A Import&acirc;ncia de Entender Pessoas</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Discutir Design </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW175149179 BCX8">Thinking</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"> &eacute; focar no entendimento das pessoas: clientes, consumidores, parceiros, influenciadores, e at&eacute; sabotadores. Somente com esse entendimento &eacute; poss&iacute;vel criar produtos, servi&ccedil;os e neg&oacute;cios que atendam &agrave;s reais necessidades dos usu&aacute;rios e stakeholders. Existem v&aacute;rias ferramentas para obter esse entendimento, e a principal delas &eacute; uma pr&aacute;tica antiga: o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">d</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">i&aacute;logo.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">A </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">a</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">rte do </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">d</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">i&aacute;logo</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Conversar parece simples, mas &eacute; mais complexo do que aparenta. Observando as in&uacute;meras ideias geradas na plataforma </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW175149179 BCX8">Avantt.i</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">, notamos uma dificuldade geral em criar uma conex&atilde;o aut&ecirc;ntica e imparcial com as pessoas para entender profundamente seu contexto e necessidades. N&atilde;o estamos falando de entrevistas r&aacute;pidas com question&aacute;rios fechados, mas de conversas profundas que duram 30 minutos ou mais, permitindo uma verdadeira imers&atilde;o no contexto estudado.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Essas conversas s&atilde;o catalisador</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">a</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">s excelentes </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">de</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"> aprendizado, ajudando a validar oportunidades ou a entender se determinada dire&ccedil;&atilde;o faz sentido, com um baixo investimento de tempo e recursos em compara&ccedil;&atilde;o com grandes pilotos que podem custar milh&otilde;es. Precisamos reaprender a ter boas conversas, uma habilidade essencial para equipes de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o avan&ccedil;arem na cria&ccedil;&atilde;o e execu&ccedil;&atilde;o de novas solu&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">Dois Modelos de Entrevistas no Design </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW175149179 BCX8">Thinking</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
<p><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Prancheta-1-4.png" width="815" height="415"></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>No processo de design, utilizamos entrevistas em diversos momentos, especialmente no in&iacute;cio e no final, cada um com objetivos diferentes. O conceito do "Diamante Duplo" do Design </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW175149179 BCX8">Thinking</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"> ilustra essas etapas, desde o entendimento do problema at&eacute; a solu&ccedil;&atilde;o. Os modelos de entrevistas variam conforme o momento, objetivo e poss&iacute;veis resultados, </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW175149179 BCX8">tangibilizando</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"> seu uso pr&aacute;tico.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/20200925_Startups-e-Corporacoes_Chart-02-1-1024x555.png" alt="Design Thinking: diferen&ccedil;as entre os tipos de entrevista." width="646" height="350"></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">Cinco Boas Pr&aacute;ticas para Executar Entrevistas</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Realizar boas entrevistas exige t&eacute;cnica e tempo. As dicas a seguir buscam incentivar a pr&aacute;tica das entrevistas mais do que "capacitar" os interessados:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="list" start="1">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="26" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">Olhar </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">n</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">eutro:</span></span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"><strong> </strong>Observe situa&ccedil;&otilde;es rotineiras com neutralidade, como um extraterrestre aprendendo tudo do zero. Isso &eacute; vital, especialmente para equipes que j&aacute; est&atilde;o no campo, permitindo um olhar sem vi&eacute;s.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="list" start="2">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="26" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">Evitar </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">p</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">erguntas </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">d</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">iretas no </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">i</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">n&iacute;cio:</span></span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"> Perguntas diretas podem enviesar a conversa. Comece explorando o problema/contexto, permitindo que as necessidades e dores emerjam naturalmente. Evite perguntas de "sim ou n&atilde;o".</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="list" start="3">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="26" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">Compreender as </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">c</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">ausas:</span></span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"> Entenda as causas dos problemas mencionados. Solu&ccedil;&otilde;es que abordam as causas-raiz, em vez dos sintomas, s&atilde;o geralmente mais eficazes e inovadoras.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="list" start="4">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="26" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">Observar o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">a</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">mbiente:</span></span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"> V&aacute; al&eacute;m da fala e da escuta: observe o ambiente e o contexto. Isso pode fornecer insights valiosos e ajudar a identificar novas perguntas durante a entrevista.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="list" start="5">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="26" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="5" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">N&atilde;o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">b</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">uscar </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">r</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">elev&acirc;ncia </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">e</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">stat&iacute;stica:</span></span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"> Entrevistas em profundidade s&atilde;o qualitativas, capturando novos insights e entendendo problemas complexos. N&atilde;o as use para obter percentuais de respostas; isso limita o potencial de descoberta.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8">A Mudan&ccedil;a de Paradigma</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
<p><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Prancheta-2-1-1024x512.png" alt="Design Thinking: Um caminho que direciona para mudan&ccedil;as." width="702" height="351"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Realizar boas entrevistas em profundidade requer uma mente aberta para novas informa&ccedil;&otilde;es, mesmo que contrariem conhecimentos estabelecidos. Isso &eacute; fundamental para a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o: novas perspectivas para resolver desafios complexos de neg&oacute;cios de forma aut&ecirc;ntica e inovadora.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175149179 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW175149179 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Mais intera&ccedil;&otilde;es reais e menos apresenta&ccedil;&otilde;es intermin&aacute;veis em escrit&oacute;rios. Isso &eacute; <strong>#design</strong> para a <strong>#inova&ccedil;&atilde;o</strong>.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW175149179 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<h3>Sobre a Avantt.i&nbsp;</h3>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>A Avantt.i &eacute; uma plataforma de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o desenvolvida pela Inventta, para gestores de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o e gerentes de projeto.</p>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Com m&oacute;dulos de intra, open e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio, oferecemos uma vis&atilde;o completa da Gest&atilde;o da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o para alavancar suas iniciativas.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Vis&atilde;o global e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio: </strong>Atrav&eacute;s da consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o, a Avantt.i ajuda a identificar os principais projetos e avan&ccedil;ar com assertividade. Tudo em uma &uacute;nica plataforma.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Programa de intra: </strong>Crie desafios e obtenha participa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos colaboradores. A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o vira rotina e voc&ecirc; impulsiona a cultura de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o na empresa.</li>
<li><strong>Open Innovation:</strong> Chame startups e parceiros para desafios, gerencie parceria na plataforma e tenha acesso a mais de 23.000 startups na nossa base.</li>
<li><strong>M&eacute;tricas Acion&aacute;veis: </strong>Influencie a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o a investir em esfor&ccedil;os de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o com base em m&eacute;tricas claras e acion&aacute;veis. Me&ccedil;a resultados dos projetos e comunique o sucesso das iniciativas</li>
